{"tid":608102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞典外交部染紅！已將台灣區域由中華民國改為中國台灣省！！","createTime":"2018-03-28T01:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T03:18:04.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"927423c8345aa3b4d4ba9c65806d9caf2d761399","tid":608102,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T01:32:20.000Z","msg":"瑞典稅務局今年2月底發布公告，將對台稱呼改為「台灣，中國一省」。雖然外界猜測，瑞典政府是在中國施壓下更改對我國稱呼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但該國政府始終不願承認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。一名駐台的瑞典記者特地追查改名的幕後原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，發現政府部門一個推一個，最後不得不難堪承認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，原來瑞典政府已屈服於北京的獨裁政權之下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180326/640_8d01a70a2cda6dd3d748b76e3c8e426c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180326%2F640_8d01a70a2cda6dd3d748b76e3c8e426c.jpg&h=60388d8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180326/1322347/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180326%2F1322347%2F&d=1MCoT%2FhTd4kw4BoMO5Iu%2FUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=d8fb2d4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180326%2F1322347%2F&h=4bd2c297\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180326/1322347/</a></div>"},{"pid":"e80d9b3d68f30a3cffbc2a188060ac618a85e9e5","tid":608102,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T01:32:48.000Z","msg":"自由撰述記者歐森（Jojje Olsson）今天在《守望台灣》網站上發表這段「落落長」的調查過程。歐森詳細列出他向瑞典稅務局及外交部的查證經過，發現兩單位的回答前後說法不一，最後他整理出所獲得的答案4重點：<br />\n<br />\n1.瑞典外交部接獲「公眾質疑」關切台灣的正式名稱。<br />\n<br />\n2.外交部聯絡國稅局及其他單位，建議把「中華民國（台灣）」改成「台灣，中國一省」<br />\n<br />\n3. 更改名稱的說法是，根據外交部的建議「修正翻譯」<br />\n<br />\n4. 原本外交部的更改名稱說法一改再改。<br />\n原本瑞典稅務局的說法是，瑞典根據ISO國家代碼及瑞典公用名稱稱呼各國，注意到台灣不符合相關形式，因此將原先「中華民國（台灣）」改為「台灣，中國一省」。"},{"pid":"0ed49506b588ff8b8794a6eefd49c5e88a2b133b","tid":608102,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T01:33:03.000Z","msg":"歐森在文中表示，任何想追查真相的人，到最後會發現，整起事件「將永無止盡地成為行政官僚間互推皮球事件，而瑞典政府體系本應是開放且透明的」。歐森還說，他和他的其他瑞典記者同僚都難堪的發現，「瑞典竟然服從在北京獨裁政權的壓力下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」。"},{"pid":"3a1b1e3db4505cb36297965b2de12f177f731653","tid":608102,"uid":63909,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T01:34:15.000Z","msg":"左膠政權"},{"pid":"70c71f5f02193ad1a0aed74b05324fbb8cf72a73","tid":608102,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T02:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0b1711c75963c9f72cc4818823ba634444642e","tid":608102,"uid":99568,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T02:03:17.000Z","msg":"所以咪話社會主義嘅國家全部都係垃圾， 包括連登仔成日吹捧嘅 瑞典"},{"pid":"915497a469d4039356f52c2b8a04698728622fe8","tid":608102,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T02:26:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f83703dcf3c1aad5d7214e3ae9cf4e92784fb7","tid":608102,"uid":59832,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:05:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2k8tkhm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2k8tkhm.png&h=9d940aa8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4bd18f52ee44260f3bf6665085850b714eb32c7f","tid":608102,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:08:48.000Z","msg":"抵比蛔殖民"},{"pid":"c4317065a39a268949c6d5cb9ef5793479c7f871","tid":608102,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:09:25.000Z","msg":"好多西方國家根本唔care台灣問題<br />\n只有美國最重視"},{"pid":"f5096b734e4d3d69c5729fdc122ba0d0bb2cc139","tid":608102,"uid":3223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4317065a39a268949c6d5cb9ef5793479c7f871","tid":608102,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:09:25.000Z","msg":"好多西方國家根本唔care台灣問題<br />\n只有美國最重視"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:11:44.000Z","msg":"而美國正視都係為咗牽制共狗<br />\n講真 人地國家，冇利益真係彩你都傻"},{"pid":"bf0223ca84ab912c5f5ad84153c636a9c3a17c6b","tid":608102,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:18:04.000Z","msg":"希望多d 蛔強姦瑞典女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}